sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as ML Model / Client
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS edge
    participant FS as Feature Server<br/>6566/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant SM as SecurityManager<br/>(in-process)
    participant Redis as Online Store (Redis)<br/>6379/TCP TLS optional
    participant BQ as Offline Store (BigQuery)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as Feast Operator
    participant Registry as Registry REST API<br/>8001/TCP TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,Redis: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval
        Client->>Route: POST /get-online-features<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OIDC/K8s)
        Route->>FS: Forward (TLS termination)
        FS->>SM: Validate permissions<br/>Permission: READ_ONLINE
        SM-->>FS: Authorized
        FS->>Redis: Get feature values<br/>Auth: Password
        Redis-->>FS: Feature data
        FS-->>Route: JSON Response
        Route-->>Client: Feature values
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Operator,Redis: Flow 2: Feature Materialization (CronJob)
        Note right of Operator: CronJob triggers kubectl exec<br/>into Feature Server pod
        Operator->>FS: kubectl exec (ServiceAccount RBAC)
        FS->>BQ: Read offline features<br/>Auth: GCP credentials
        BQ-->>FS: Historical feature data
        FS->>Redis: Write to online store<br/>Auth: Password
        Redis-->>FS: Write confirmed
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,BQ: Flow 3: Feature Push (with offline batching)
        Client->>Route: POST /push<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Route->>FS: Forward (TLS termination)
        FS->>SM: Validate permissions<br/>Permission: WRITE_ONLINE / WRITE_OFFLINE
        SM-->>FS: Authorized
        FS->>Redis: Write to online store
        Redis-->>FS: Write confirmed
        FS-->>Route: Push acknowledged
        Route-->>Client: 200 OK
        Note right of FS: Background thread batches<br/>offline writes (size/time flush)
        FS->>BQ: Batch write to offline store<br/>Auth: GCP credentials
    end

    rect rgb(245, 230, 255)
        Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Operator Auto-Access RBAC
        Operator->>Registry: GET /api/v1/permissions<br/>Auth: Intra-communication JWT
        Registry-->>Operator: Permission policies
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update RBAC resources<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: RBAC resources created
    end
